programme.title: Star Wars:原力觉醒 STAR WARS: EPISODE VII - THE FORCE AWAKENS
programme.desc: Evil rises from the ashes and there’s no hero to save the Empire. It is up to Rey and Finn to join forces with Hans Solo and Chewbacca to restore peace to the galaxy 邪恶力量从灰烬中崛起，却没有人可以解救帝国，如今必须仰赖沙漠拾荒者芮和叛逃的风暴兵芬恩与汉索罗及秋巴卡连手，尽全力让银河系恢复和平。.(n)

programme.title: 诱.惑 DOUBT
programme.desc: A priest's ambiguous relationship with a 12-year-old student is questioned by the school's strict principal. 弗林神父因与12岁男学生关系密切，遭到严厉的校长艾萝西丝修女的质疑。.(n)

programme.title: HBO电影介绍8 THE HBO MOVIE SHOW 08
programme.desc: Get the inside scoop on all the latest and greatest movies flying out of Hollywood on The HBO Movie Show. 本节目提供好莱坞最新及最大制作电影的精彩内幕消息。.(n)

programme.title: 猪头晚餐 DINNER FOR SCHMUCKS
programme.desc: An extraordinarily stupid man possesses the ability to ruin the life of anyone who spends more than a few minutes in his company. 提姆即将升迁，他首度受老板之邀前往参加每个月一次的「猪头晚餐」，这个由老板主办的晚餐，旨在让大家尽情吹嘘。.(n)

programme.title: 布偶奇遇记 FRAGGLE ROCK S3 09: THE SECRET SOCIETY OF POOHBAHS
programme.desc: Mokey is asked to join the Secret Society of Poohbahs. She immediately breaks the first rule and has to undergo a trial. 玛吉受邀加入神秘的布巴社团，但她一下就破坏规定，必须接受审判。.(n)

programme.title: 汉克大冒险 HANK ZIPZER S3 07: UNDERCOVER HANK
programme.desc: Mr Love returns to the school and Hank is forced to dress up as a girl in order to catch someone trying to frame him. 乐夫校长回来学校；此时汉克为了揪出陷害他的人而假扮成女生。.(n)

programme.title: 汉克大冒险 HANK ZIPZER S3 08: SCHOOL SLEEPOVER
programme.desc: Hank is looking forward to Mr Rock’s sponsored school sleepover where he intends to retrieve his gift for Rosa… from the bin. 汉克要送给妈妈的礼物被阿朵夫老师丢到垃圾桶，他决定要利用洛克老师举办的过夜营队偷偷把它拿回来。.(n)

programme.title: 超级8 SUPER 8
programme.desc: A catastrophic train crash, unusual disappearances and inexplicable events take place in a small Ohio town, and in time culminate in a devastatingly terrifying event. 1979年夏天，俄亥俄小镇一群青少年在拍摄「超级8」电影其间目睹一场火车意外发生，他们长大后开始怀疑，当年的事件并不是意外，而他们生活也接二连三出现不可思议奇异事件。.(n)

programme.title: 金龟车贺比:全速前进 HERBIE: FULLY LOADED
programme.desc: A freewheelin' Volkswagen bug with a mind of its own is on his way to becoming a Nascar champion! 一辆拥有自我意志的福斯金龟车正朝向全国运动汽车竞赛协会(Nascar)的冠军奖杯前进！.(n)

programme.title: 星际大奇航 THE HITCHHIKER'S GUIDE TO THE GALAXY
programme.desc: The story of a guy named Arthur Dent who one day wakes up only to find that his friend is an alien. 阿瑟丹特某日一觉醒来竟面临可怕的事件，他得知好友竟是外星人，而地球即将要被毁灭….(n)

programme.title: 怒海漂流S1:01 SAFE HARBOUR S1 01
programme.desc: Five Australians on a yacht help a boatload of asylum seekers by towing them. With seven deaths, a mystery that reignites several years later, when they meet again. 五个澳洲人驾着游艇拖曳载满难民的船，试着救援这些难民。然而连接两船的绳索却被切断，导致七人死亡，这个未解的谜团在数年后他们再度相遇之时仍然疑云重重。.(n)

programme.title: 挫折的女人 REAL WOMEN HAVE CURVES
programme.desc: A young Hispanic woman must choose between ambition and tradition in this coming of age comedy where real women embrace life...and have curves. 父母是墨西哥移民，而她出生在洛杉矶，一方面希望能上大学，当个现代女性，但也面临传统文化的压力。女主角有血有泪，她并不完美，但她拥抱人生！.(n)

programme.title: 龙兄鼠弟 TWINS
programme.desc: Arnold Schwarzenegger and Danny DeVito team up as a pair of mismatched twins separated at birth who reunite to look for their missing mum. 本片是阿诺从影以来演出最成功的喜剧,绝对能令您捧腹开怀。故事述说六个人自愿参加一项创造完美人类的试验，但结果代理孕母生出的不是一个完美的小孩，而是一对双胞胎。.(n)

programme.title: 杀戮时刻 A TIME TO KILL
programme.desc: A murder trial brings a small town's racial tensions to the flashpoint while an unseasoned but idealistic young attorney mounts a stirring courtroom battle for justice. 年轻有理想的新手律师登上法庭为正义奋战，而这起谋杀案很可能将引爆小镇的种族冲突。.(n)

programme.title: 女飞贼杰特S1:04 JETT S1 04: FRANK SWEENEY
programme.desc: Jett tracks down a brutal gangster she and Blair worked for ten years earlier. 刚从牢里出来的世界级窃盗高手黛西”洁特＂科沃斯基被迫重操旧业，而一群行事诡异的罪犯纷纷想利用她…….(n)

programme.title: 诡影豪宅 DELIRIUM
programme.desc: A man recently released from a mental institute encounters a series of mysterious events and he attempts to figure out if these happenings are real or delirium. 刚从精神病院出院的男子遭遇一连串的神秘事件，他努力厘清这一切是真实发生还是精神错乱的结果。.(n)

programme.title: 西瓜甜不甜 Say Cheese - EP 7
programme.desc: (R) Ze Guo suspects Ke Lin of having an affair and secretly follows him. Ke Lin realises he is being followed and shakes Ze Guo off by making it look like it is all a misunderstanding. However, Ke Lin does in fact have a mistress named Xiao Rou. Xiao Rou prepares an art studio for him to chase his dream of becoming an artist. Ke Lin is moved. Being under the pressure of Ze Guo this whole time, he is able to find comfort when being with Xiao Rou.
